export enum VesStatus {
    ACTIVE = "Active",
    ON_HOLD = "On Hold",
    COMPLETED = "Completed",
    COMPLETED_WITHOUT_PAYMENT = "Completed W/O Payment",
    DELETED_WITH_OVERPAYMENT = "Deleted with Overpayment",
    DELETED_WITHOUT_OVERPAYMENT = "Deleted without Overpayment",
    PENDING_APPROVAL = "-",
    PENDING_EDIT_APPROVAL = "-",
    PENDING_DELETE_APPROVAL = "-"
}

export enum RequestStatus {
    PENDING_APPROVAL = "Pending Approval",
    APPROVED = "Approved",
    REJECTED = "Rejected"
}

export enum VesStatusMenu {
    ACTIVE = "Active",
    ON_HOLD = "On Hold",
    COMPLETED = "Completed",
    COMPLETED_WITHOUT_PAYMENT = "Completed W/O Payment",
    DELETED_WITH_OVERPAYMENT = "Deleted with Overpayment",
    DELETED_WITHOUT_OVERPAYMENT = "Deleted without Overpayment",
    PENDING_APPROVAL = "Pending Approval",
    PENDING_EDIT_APPROVAL = "Pending Edit Approval",
    PENDING_DELETE_APPROVAL = "Pending Delete Approval"
}
